window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Enjoy this collection of Battle Mage books 4-6</b></p> <p>I have been separated by my companions, left far to the north of civilization. My quest is a simple one: Find a dragon and bond with it. However simple this quest may seem, it is exceedingly difficult.</p> <p>Not only that, but my companions have been called to the goblin city of Geriarc to do battle with the undead, led by shadowlords.</p> <p>All the while, evil festers in the Jade Bastion.</p> <p>First things first; I must tame a dragon, then I will deal with the undead scourge and the evil that has taken root in my new home.</p>"; 
